description:
My Absence
Original Air Date: February 10, 2009 - Directed by: John Putch - Written by: Debra Fordham & Andy Schwartz 

    * J.D. is away on a vacation, which makes Elliot miss him and Dr. Cox happy.
    * Carla tells Turk that she is pregnant again, but nobody is excited except for him and Elliot.
    * Sunny doesn't find any help when she tries to keep a brain-dead patient alive.
